 🌤️ Weather App UI Design

A | Weather App |  UI design built using | HTML | and | CSS | This project focuses on creating a clean and responsive user interface for displaying weather information. The app is ready to be connected with a backend API to fetch real-time weather data.

---

📋 Features

- 🌆 Clean and modern design for displaying weather data
- 🖥️ Fully responsive layout for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
- ☀️ Displays weather information like temperature, humidity, and weather condition icons
- 🎨 Minimalistic UI with clear visual hierarchy
- 🌈 Flexible design that can be easily integrated with a weather API for dynamic data fetching

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- | HTML5 | – For the structure and markup
- | CSS3 | – For styling and responsive design

